Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about automatic speech recognition (ASR) systems and language modeling.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with acoustic modeling and encoding.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses model design, pretraining schemes, training schedules, and optimization approaches.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as ASR is a subfield of AI.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the development of ASR systems using open-source toolkits.
